<span class="code-comment">-- Child calling parent method</span>
<span class="code-keyword">self</span>:<span class="code-type">callParentMethod</span>(<span class="code-string">"handleUserAction"</span>, ws_id, { action = <span class="code-string">"login"</span> })</code></pre>
